nd','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Tap: Erhöhe Deinen Manavorrat um R oder B. Diese Karte zählt als Gebirge und als Sumpf und unterliegt Zaubersprüchen, die für diese beiden Standard-Länder gelten. Zerstört ein Zauberspruch eine dieser Standard-Länder, wird diese Karte zerstört; verändert ein Zauberspruch eines dieser Standard-Länder, bleibt das andere Standard-Land davon unberührt.','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('1329','Balance','R','Sorcery','R','{1}{W}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Each player chooses a number of lands they control equal to the number of lands controlled by the player who controls the fewest, then sacrifices the rest. Players discard cards and sacrifice creatures the same way.',NULL,NULL,'Mark Poole','187','4.901','£6/8/2016: First the player whose turn it is chooses which lands (if any) to keep, then each other player in turn order does the same. Each player will know the choices made by the players who chose before them. All of the unchosen lands are then sacrificed simultaneously. Then the process is repeated for cards in hand, except that no cards are revealed until all players have chosen what to discard, at which point those cards are all discarded simultaneously. Lastly, the process is repeated for creatures, and players will again know earlier choices made when deciding what to sacrifice. All of the unchosen creatures are then sacrificed simultaneously.£6/8/2016: Balance doesn’t have targets, so permanents that can’t be targeted, such as a creature with shroud or protection from white, are valid choices to be sacrificed.£6/8/2016: Each type of object is counted during the corresponding part of the process. Cards in hand are counted after lands have been sacrificed, and creatures on the battlefield are counted after cards have been discarded. Thus, a land creature sacrificed to the first part of the spell would not be counted when determining how many creatures are on the battlefield for the last part.','W',NULL,'0.94','1.61','10',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,'Balance','Balance','Bilancia dell''Equilibrio',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Hexerei','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Alle Spieler opfern so viele Länder, bis alle Spieler gleichviele Länder im Spiel haben. Der Spieler, der die wenigsten Länder hat, darf aber jetzt keine Länder opfern. Dann gleichen alle Spieler die Anzahl der Karten, die sie auf der Hand haben und die Anzahl der Kreaturen, die sie im Spiel haben, nach der selben Methode einander an.','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('1096','Basalt Monolith','R','Artifact','U','{3}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Basalt Monolith doesn''t untap during your untap step.£{T}: Add {C}{C}{C}.£{3}: Untap Basalt Monolith.',NULL,NULL,'Jesper Myrfors','235','3.688','£10/4/2004: It can be untapped as often as you can pay for it.','A','{C}','0.67','1.33','5.45',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Monolithe de basalte','Basaltmonolith','Monolito di Basalto',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Artefakt','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Tap: Erhöhe Deinen Manavorrat um 3 farblose Mana. Spiele diese Eigenschaft wie einen Unterbrechungszauber. Der Basaltmonolith kann während Deiner Enttap-Phase nicht normal enttappt werden. Das Enttappen zu jeder anderen Zeit kostet Dich 3. Du kannst allerdings dafür nicht das Mana verwenden, dass Du vom Monolithen bekommen hast.','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('1377','Bayou','R','Land — Swamp Forest','R',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_({T}: Add {B} or {G}.)_#',NULL,NULL,'Jesper Myrfors','283','4.837','£10/1/2008: This has the mana abilities associated with both of its basic land types.£10/1/2008: Th